WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.360 --> 00:00:01.800
Well, will you look at this.

2
00:00:01.800 --> 00:00:05.280
Right there in the sent items
 there's a message that was sent 9:00 a.m.

3
00:00:05.280 --> 00:00:06.840
this morning, But

4
00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:10.640
DCI Crooks was arrested in the early hours
 so that couldn't have been her.

5
00:00:10.640 --> 00:00:13.040
We need to get this to the CPS
 as soon as possible.

6
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:16.200
Select
 the message, encrypt it and send it off.

7
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:20.360
I know that CPS use the Mega Encryption
 Technology software to make sure

8
00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:21.160
it's secure.

9
00:00:21.160 --> 00:00:23.720
I'll email through instructions
 on how to use it.

10
00:00:24.720 --> 00:00:27.320
Get this done
 and it'll be tea and medals for us all.

